A motorcycle rider died yesterday in Kirinyaga County.
The victim, who is yet to be identified, was heading towards Kutus from Ngurubani area when he was killed in a hit-and-run incident.
According to witnesses, the rider was going uphill when he was hit from behind in Nyangati Village. He died on the spot at around 12.30 am.



